00:22:01,050 --> 00:22:02,920
Now, I am back,

295
00:22:04,310 --> 00:22:06,400
yet I often think of

296
00:22:07,170 --> 00:22:09,320
the days in Chang’an.

297
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:13,280
Maybe that’s human nature,

298
00:22:13,280 --> 00:22:15,690
always clinging

299
00:22:15,690 --> 00:22:17,070
on to the past.

300
00:22:21,790 --> 00:22:22,680
What about you?

301
00:22:24,540 --> 00:22:26,560
Judging from your figure and stride,

302
00:22:27,340 --> 00:22:29,050
you should be quite young.

303
00:22:30,470 --> 00:22:34,360
Why are you living in seclusion?

304
00:22:37,240 --> 00:22:38,800
Because nothing

305
00:22:40,180 --> 00:22:41,120
is valuable to me

306
00:22:41,120 --> 00:22:42,510
in this busy world anymore.

307
00:22:45,110 --> 00:22:46,710
It is too early

308
00:22:47,420 --> 00:22:49,480
to draw a conclusion to your life.

309
00:22:52,870 --> 00:22:54,410
Some people’s lives

310
00:22:56,190 --> 00:22:58,290
can be easily anticipated.

311
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:04,650
Your Highness,

312
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:07,070
should I do the acupuncture now?

313
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:39,740
Assassin!

314
00:23:59,700 --> 00:24:00,790
Chun.

315
00:24:02,190 --> 00:24:03,320
Protect His Highness.

316
00:24:05,930 --> 00:24:07,020
Princess Yuan Chun.

317
00:24:08,150 --> 00:24:08,820
Your Highness...

318
00:24:09,980 --> 00:24:10,940
Leave.

319
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:12,280
Your Highness!

320
00:24:15,660 --> 00:24:16,360
Leave.

321
00:24:16,360 --> 00:24:17,110
- Aye.
- Aye.

322
00:24:29,150 --> 00:24:29,880
You...

323
00:24:40,010 --> 00:24:41,010
Just go.

324
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:43,990
Chun.

325
00:24:48,230 --> 00:24:49,220
I am sorry.

326
00:24:55,110 --> 00:24:56,550
Take care.

