♪ You fly high ♪

333
00:25:39,950 --> 00:25:41,450
♪ I fall hard ♪

334
00:25:41,450 --> 00:25:42,950
If you leave Chang’an,

335
00:25:43,100 --> 00:25:43,900
where could you find

336
00:25:43,900 --> 00:25:45,600
so much fine liquor,

337
00:25:45,980 --> 00:25:48,140
and a beauty like me?

338
00:25:48,140 --> 00:25:48,810
♪ Tears could be held back ♪

339
00:25:48,810 --> 00:25:50,920
♪ The night is still dark ♪

340
00:25:50,920 --> 00:25:52,200
We have grown up together.

341
00:25:52,540 --> 00:25:53,210
I swear

342
00:25:53,210 --> 00:25:53,680
♪ Being mature means to stop dreaming ♪

343
00:25:53,680 --> 00:25:54,750
I will protect you.

344
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:56,110
You’ll always be my sister.

345
00:25:56,110 --> 00:25:58,510
