00:27:11,220 --> 00:27:13,300
= To Your Highness =

364
00:27:18,480 --> 00:27:19,510
Your Highness,

365
00:27:20,220 --> 00:27:22,450
are you still hesitating
about sending the army?

366
00:27:28,460 --> 00:27:29,930
Do you have any advice?

367
00:27:31,610 --> 00:27:33,150
Your Highness should know

368
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:34,860
that letter is fake.

369
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:42,650
In the letter...

370
00:27:43,890 --> 00:27:46,090
The handwriting and wording

371
00:27:47,250 --> 00:27:49,280
are of Yuwen Yue’s style.

372
00:27:49,390 --> 00:27:50,900
I can’t tell the difference.

373
00:27:52,880 --> 00:27:55,550
The problem doesn’t lie
in those two aspects

374
00:27:56,060 --> 00:27:57,560
but the content.

375
00:28:02,060 --> 00:28:03,490
I have placed some scouts

376
00:28:03,490 --> 00:28:05,190
in Yanbei.

377
00:28:07,020 --> 00:28:08,710
Were it really as serious

378
00:28:08,710 --> 00:28:10,020
as General Yuwen said in the letter,

379
00:28:10,630 --> 00:28:11,920
how could my scouts

380
00:28:11,920 --> 00:28:13,230
know nothing about it?

381
00:28:13,840 --> 00:28:15,580
Not a single message

382
00:28:15,710 --> 00:28:17,070
has been sent back.

383
00:28:18,930 --> 00:28:21,180
Maybe your scouts

384
00:28:21,510 --> 00:28:22,440
are incompetent.

385
00:28:27,740 --> 00:28:29,030
They can’t be

386
00:28:29,030 --> 00:28:30,160
that bad.

387
00:28:32,450 --> 00:28:34,910
Yanbei won the last battle

388
00:28:35,370 --> 00:28:37,320
but they also suffered huge losses.

389
00:28:39,680 --> 00:28:41,250
It’s impossible

390
00:28:42,580 --> 00:28:43,750
for Yan Xun

391
00:28:45,240 --> 00:28:47,690
to take action so soon.

392
00:28:49,070 --> 00:28:51,650
All that doesn’t matter.

393
00:28:52,270 --> 00:28:53,680
What matters is

394
00:28:56,630 --> 00:28:58,580
the benevolence

395
00:28:58,580 --> 00:29:00,170
of Your Highness.

396
00:29:00,780 --> 00:29:01,680
Your Highness,

397
00:29:02,470 --> 00:29:05,340
do you really believe
Yan Xun will surrender,

398
00:29:05,540 --> 00:29:07,480
and give up revenge?

399
00:29:10,030 --> 00:29:13,390
Your Highness, if we let this chance slip,

400
00:29:13,780 --> 00:29:16,170
thus enabling Yanbei to recuperate,

401
00:29:16,480 --> 00:29:17,720
I am afraid

402
00:29:18,030 --> 00:29:19,910
the situation will be harder

403
00:29:19,910 --> 00:29:21,530
to control then.

404
00:29:23,990 --> 00:29:25,930
The person who forged this letter

405
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:28,660
must know Your Highness
wouldn’t be fooled.

406
00:29:28,660 --> 00:29:29,930
After all,

407
00:29:30,420 --> 00:29:32,320
all you need is a

408
00:29:32,320 --> 00:29:34,040
proper excuse to convince the army

409
00:29:34,040 --> 00:29:36,420
that is haunted by the fear of war.

410
00:29:41,350 --> 00:29:42,850
You are incisive,

411
00:29:43,350 --> 00:29:45,120
as always.

412
00:29:45,320 --> 00:29:46,280
Your Highness,

413
00:29:46,500 --> 00:29:49,120
you are the future ruler.

414
00:29:49,310 --> 00:29:50,650
This empire

415
00:29:50,650 --> 00:29:53,000
is built on flesh and blood.

416
00:29:54,970 --> 00:29:55,940
Do you remember

417
00:29:55,940 --> 00:29:57,340
what you told me

418
00:29:57,340 --> 00:29:57,760
the first time

419
00:29:57,760 --> 00:29:59,110
we met?

420
00:30:04,350 --> 00:30:07,610
I said every inch of the land,

421
00:30:07,610 --> 00:30:09,140
all four seas,

422
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:13,120
the vast desert in the west,

423
00:30:14,470 --> 00:30:16,730
steeps mountains in the south,

424
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:19,700
the snow in the north,

425
00:30:20,540 --> 00:30:22,930
and the boundless sea in the east,

426
00:30:24,260 --> 00:30:26,730
will all submit to Wei.

427
00:30:26,910 --> 00:30:28,570
And all that

428
00:30:29,660 --> 00:30:32,450
starts with me.

429
00:30:35,230 --> 00:30:36,750
At this stage,

430
00:30:37,150 --> 00:30:38,930
are you still thinking the same?

431
00:30:39,630 --> 00:30:41,190
I’ve never forgotten about my ambition.

432
00:30:42,600 --> 00:30:44,140
If so,

433
00:30:45,710 --> 00:30:49,680
we will start with Yanbei.

434
00:31:04,730 --> 00:31:05,580
Let’s go!

435
00:31:24,000 --> 00:31:25,400
Yan Xun went to great lengths this time

436
00:31:25,560 --> 00:31:26,270
and leveled a dozen camps

437
00:31:26,270 --> 00:31:27,290
of ours.

438
00:31:27,930 --> 00:31:30,440
Casualties are huge.

439
00:31:31,440 --> 00:31:33,480
Young Master has been

440
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:34,250
on a winning streak lately.

441
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:36,060
Yan Xun is desperate.

442
00:31:37,270 --> 00:31:38,280
The reason

443
00:31:38,830 --> 00:31:40,200
we won is that

444
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:41,640
we got the information
about their deployment

445
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:43,550
and generals beforehand,

446
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:45,650
so we could counterattack accordingly

447
00:31:45,650 --> 00:31:46,780
and beat them one by one.

448
00:31:47,310 --> 00:31:48,650
After several times,

449
00:31:49,590 --> 00:31:50,600
they must have figured out

450
00:31:50,600 --> 00:31:51,650
what the problems are.

451
00:31:52,600 --> 00:31:54,780
Young Master, what about Yuejiu?

452
00:31:55,090 --> 00:31:56,210
The last time we got

453
00:31:56,210 --> 00:31:57,020
his information

454
00:31:57,230 --> 00:31:58,410
was at a farmer’s house

455
00:31:58,410 --> 00:31:59,470
near Xiuli Villa,

456
00:31:59,670 --> 00:32:01,150
while he was with Zhuang Qing’s children.

457
00:32:02,380 --> 00:32:03,570
Zhuang Qing’s whole family

458
00:32:03,570 --> 00:32:05,010
died in Yan Xun’s hands.

459
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:07,470
If the kids are captured...

460
00:32:10,210 --> 00:32:11,490
I will go save them.

461
00:32:12,670 --> 00:32:13,940
Please think twice, Young Master.

462
00:32:16,340 --> 00:32:17,380
They were there

463
00:32:17,790 --> 00:32:19,180
because of me.

464
00:32:19,720 --> 00:32:22,350
I cannot let anything happen to them.

465
00:32:22,840 --> 00:32:25,020
Young Master, I’ll go with you.

466
00:32:25,840 --> 00:32:26,690
No need.

467
00:32:27,330 --> 00:32:29,090
You stay and protect Prince Yu.

468
00:32:29,550 --> 00:32:30,670
Yueqi will go with me.

469
00:32:31,030 --> 00:32:31,410
Aye.

470
00:32:31,410 --> 00:32:32,090
Aye.

471
00:33:18,060 --> 00:33:22,180
= Mountain God’s Temple =

472
00:34:48,580 --> 00:34:49,700
Come on. Let’s drink.

473
00:34:49,700 --> 00:34:51,340
Come on. Fill the cup. Dig in.

474
00:34:54,550 --> 00:34:56,090
Refill. Come on.

475
00:34:56,210 --> 00:34:56,900
Come on.

476
00:35:02,220 --> 00:35:02,910
Yueqi.

477
00:35:10,940 --> 00:35:11,750
Yueqi.

478
00:35:14,950 --> 00:35:15,890
Take the two kids

479
00:35:15,890 --> 00:35:16,680
and go downhill.

480
00:35:16,850 --> 00:35:18,090
I will catch up with you.

481
00:35:18,380 --> 00:35:19,120
Young Master.

482
00:35:20,520 --> 00:35:21,230
Go.

483
00:35:21,750 --> 00:35:22,490
Aye.

484
00:35:24,890 --> 00:35:25,790
Come on. Let’s go.

485
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:26,910
Come.

486
00:35:27,340 --> 00:35:27,920
Let’s go.

487
00:35:45,260 --> 00:35:47,010
You came in the nick of time.

488
00:35:47,700 --> 00:35:49,360
What a coincidence!

489
00:35:49,360 --> 00:35:50,420
Eat with me.

490
00:35:55,340 --> 00:35:56,140
What happened?

491
00:35:56,730 --> 00:35:58,390
Meilin Pass doesn’t welcome you,

492
00:35:58,390 --> 00:35:59,660
so you came here to eat?

493
00:36:02,390 --> 00:36:04,080
This place belongs to Yanbei.

494
00:36:04,080 --> 00:36:05,720
And you are wanted here.

495
00:36:06,990 --> 00:36:08,460
Aren’t you afraid that I will capture you?

496
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:11,520
If you want, just go ahead.

497
00:36:18,230 --> 00:36:19,550
Come on, it’s still hot.

498
00:36:21,820 --> 00:36:23,070
This is God’s temple.

499
00:36:23,430 --> 00:36:24,760
Eating isn’t allowed.

500
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:26,740
You can watch me eat.

501
00:36:35,130 --> 00:36:36,500
I thought you don’t drink.

502
00:36:39,780 --> 00:36:41,220
Things have changed.

503
00:36:41,650 --> 00:36:42,590
Now, I actually think

504
00:36:42,590 --> 00:36:43,970
liquor is a cure.

505
00:36:44,370 --> 00:36:46,100
It helps put trouble behind.

506
00:37:00,930 --> 00:37:03,490
Let me toast you.

507
00:37:04,210 --> 00:37:05,870
Thank you for helping me over and over.

508
00:37:24,870 --> 00:37:25,630
So,

509
00:37:26,870 --> 00:37:28,030
what are you here for?

510
00:37:31,530 --> 00:37:32,930
Not for you for sure.

511
00:37:33,400 --> 00:37:34,240
I know

512
00:37:34,240 --> 00:37:34,990
you didn’t come here for me.

513
00:37:35,820 --> 00:37:36,870
Under your watch, Meilin Pass

514
00:37:36,870 --> 00:37:37,910
is impregnable

515
00:37:38,450 --> 00:37:40,030
and you’ve beat back Yan Xun’s attacks

516
00:37:40,030 --> 00:37:41,440
several times with fewer troops.

517
00:37:42,180 --> 00:37:43,290
Right now, at Meilin Pass,

518
00:37:43,290 --> 00:37:44,540
you’re in your pomp.

519
00:37:44,700 --> 00:37:46,130
Ladies from prominent families there

520
00:37:46,130 --> 00:37:47,440
have been throwing themselves at you.

521
00:37:47,550 --> 00:37:49,000
How could you still think of me?

522
00:37:50,470 --> 00:37:51,350
People change

523
00:37:52,220 --> 00:37:54,090
with time.

524
00:37:55,110 --> 00:37:56,700
They have started to
know their limitations.

525
00:37:59,630 --> 00:38:00,670
But don’t worry.

526
00:38:02,350 --> 00:38:04,650
As Xiao Ce said,

527
00:38:05,140 --> 00:38:07,550
I always have bad taste.

528
00:38:08,340 --> 00:38:10,130
Those ladies

529
00:38:10,240 --> 00:38:12,570
are beautiful, fit

530
00:38:12,570 --> 00:38:13,610
and well-educated.

531
00:38:14,380 --> 00:38:15,840
But they aren’t my type.

532
00:38:18,550 --> 00:38:20,250
I heard that you got promoted.

533
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:21,460
Yes.

534
00:38:22,510 --> 00:38:24,080
I defended Hongchuan

535
00:38:24,080 --> 00:38:25,140
and killed Yuan Qi.

536
00:38:26,560 --> 00:38:28,060
That’s enough for a promotion.

537
00:38:28,730 --> 00:38:30,130
But I also heard

538
00:38:30,300 --> 00:38:32,850
that Xiuli Army had been abolished.

539
00:38:33,850 --> 00:38:36,140
It’s no longer part of the Yanbei Troops.

540
00:38:36,510 --> 00:38:38,160
Even their use of weapons

541
00:38:38,620 --> 00:38:39,900
is restricted.

542
00:38:40,370 --> 00:38:41,850
Xiuli Army has been reassigned to

543
00:38:41,850 --> 00:38:42,570
Xiuli Mountain

544
00:38:42,570 --> 00:38:43,770
and answers to the local government.

545
00:38:43,770 --> 00:38:44,790
It’s natural

546
00:38:44,790 --> 00:38:45,980
to restrict the weapons.

547
00:38:46,400 --> 00:38:47,870
But I heard

548
00:38:48,160 --> 00:38:49,430
that Zhao Gui had sent his family members

549
00:38:49,430 --> 00:38:50,650
to Meilin Pass

550
00:38:51,010 --> 00:38:52,950
to separate your powers.

551
00:38:54,280 --> 00:38:55,720
People always make wishes.

552
00:38:56,240 --> 00:38:57,280
Whether they can be realized or not

553
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:58,650
is another story.

554
00:39:00,090 --> 00:39:02,310
Zhong Yu is confined to Lancheng.

555
00:39:03,540 --> 00:39:05,000
I’m quite curious

556
00:39:06,220 --> 00:39:07,460
about the reason.

557
00:39:08,550 --> 00:39:09,600
There are always some little hassles

558
00:39:09,600 --> 00:39:10,850
within every organization.

559
00:39:11,390 --> 00:39:13,540
You’ve been through ups and downs, right?

560
00:39:15,050 --> 00:39:15,990
Besides,

561
00:39:16,330 --> 00:39:18,130
what you heard isn’t necessarily true.

562
00:39:19,040 --> 00:39:20,670
Just like I heard

563
00:39:21,820 --> 00:39:24,620
that the Death Camp has changed sides

564
00:39:25,620 --> 00:39:27,530
and merged into the Eye of Intel.

565
00:39:30,400 --> 00:39:32,700
Those rats

566
00:39:33,310 --> 00:39:34,410
are everywhere.

567
00:39:35,860 --> 00:39:37,150
They know almost everything

568
00:39:37,150 --> 00:39:38,180
in the world.

569
00:39:39,960 --> 00:39:41,070
As for the things

570
00:39:41,070 --> 00:39:42,340
you have investigated for long,

571
00:39:44,330 --> 00:39:46,560
have you got answers with their help?

572
00:39:48,140 --> 00:39:50,440
Hearsay bears no credibility.

573
00:39:52,290 --> 00:39:53,850
I heard Mr. Wu is back.

574
00:39:54,330 --> 00:39:55,480
Have you met with him?

575
00:39:57,700 --> 00:40:00,230
Mr. Wu is erudite

576
00:40:00,400 --> 00:40:01,630
and skilled at medicine.

577
00:40:02,120 --> 00:40:04,180
Have you regained your memory?

578
00:40:05,160 --> 00:40:06,550
Have you figured out

579
00:40:06,550 --> 00:40:07,790
where you’re from

580
00:40:07,930 --> 00:40:08,840
and who you are?

581
00:40:09,610 --> 00:40:11,380
Mind your own business.

582
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:13,310
You do have some prestige

583
00:40:13,310 --> 00:40:14,360
at Meilin Pass,

584
00:40:14,360 --> 00:40:15,460
but tons of people

585
00:40:15,460 --> 00:40:16,470
can’t wait to take you down.

586
00:40:17,240 --> 00:40:18,630
The eight tribes

587
00:40:18,630 --> 00:40:20,970
